{"tid":1494914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[幫推]今日三點 中學生反修例集會 (已獲不反對通知書）","createTime":"2019-08-22T00:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T14:25:17.000Z","uid":61520,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7af99fc1a1258c59c198ee083c4a9fbb21672cdf","tid":1494914,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:00:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日三點！<br />\n聽日三點！<br />\n聽日三點！<br />\n<br />\n愛丁堡廣場！<br />\n<br />\n中學生反修例集會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已獲不反對通知書！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋係班自發組織嘅中學生群體，當日我哋主要係想透過呢個集會黎團結一群中學生嘅力量。 <br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候，已經出現左大大小小，不同專業界別，不同年齡層嘅市民因為社會中的不公義而發聲；但係！呢位特首依然冇因為我哋嘅聲音而作出任何實際行動解決現時困局！我地只係班中學生，係能力及經驗不足嘅情況下仍被逼要企出黎對抗社會不公義！當我地被某啲人指責不應該嘅時候， 尤其係屋企人唔支持情況下心靈受着極大壓力下仲企出黎抗爭。我哋係好需要屋企人嘅支持。特首口口聲聲話香嘅港未來係屬於 年輕人。但就用<span style=\"color: red;\">非人道而且極之殘忍手法去對待打壓我哋</span>。令到好多年輕人為之而受到不必要傷害、流血甚至輕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n而我哋今次自發集會目的係想建立一個平台， 讓不同人士， 尤其係中學生更了解呢件事，而且保持一個理性，和平，多角度以及批判性思考黎討論事件。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地希望<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月22號（今日下午3點）愛丁堡廣場</span></span><br />\n屆時會有嘉賓分享，社工心靈輔導，師生小組等等。<br />\n<br />\nLast but not least, 希望不論中學生定任何人士都希望你黎，就算唔支持都可以坐低理性討論。黎得嘅就代表有心為香港社會 矛盾解決。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港核心，法治民主！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n一群來自不同學校的中學生"},{"pid":"53cef6c21c30edce29880d2fdc7b70e670f95e21","tid":1494914,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:01:34.000Z","msg":"source from<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">再唔入黎就死人！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494790</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7eb8c9575d185ee896cb9b77d11855090674ddbb","tid":1494914,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3834ff52ebbb7b008b8ca5bbce08964707e25b6c","tid":1494914,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d62323ce2c8d4dc3a1e79c3ba0ef92a68e63938","tid":1494914,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:12:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81e5864507c28713be4652abbe916160d3d543f6","tid":1494914,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:12:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"927a7297620b94c78d80c6866564f0b7139fc699","tid":1494914,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b2814afb6cae812edc6ab30a1cc817860e37d02","tid":1494914,"uid":3424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4601f6dca262d880bf049dbaaa94c6590e9f6d","tid":1494914,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:13:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1859fbb27bec2c3b74deb79d9e2cabd90b18e10","tid":1494914,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:14:11.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"b883947886dfabb157d66640a2472b8c2405f52e","tid":1494914,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:15:05.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 不過入黎表態支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c730591cc6cf9fe7c3c6dd412eb01eece9a6a8f","tid":1494914,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T00:17:26.000Z","msg":"同學加油"},{"pid":"